"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Because of the responsibility, Wu Fen of the candle, regardless of the body and wisdom, retired from Qin division; Because of his responsibility, Jing Ke did not hesitate to assassinate the king of Qin; Because of responsibility, Ba Jin deeply repents and awakens human nature... Throughout the ages, how many heroes have interpreted responsibility with actions and tortured the soul with words.\\n\\n \\n\\nEternal candle power\\n\\n \\n\\nThe waning moon is like a knife and the night is like ink. A staggering old man is walking towards us. It is autumn now. The bleak autumn wind is blowing the silver hair at that end. He, the martial arts of candle, did not have much words or fear. Just because of the national crisis, he resolutely stood up and said to retreat from the Qin army, which is known as the \\\"division of tigers and wolves\\\". Die in national disaster, and die suddenly. He is a piece of the gold that never speaks. He interprets responsibility with the his actions. Eternal candle power!\\n\\n \\n\\nResponsibility, let us not turn back.\\n\\n \\n\\nJing Ke assassinates King Qin\\n\\n \\n\\nThe cold wind is biting, you say: the wind is rustling, the water is cold, and the strong man will never return once he goes. How many people's heartstrings have been stirred. In the face of danger, you are fearless and calm. Yi Shui said goodbye. You took your water cold sword and pointed directly at the blue sky: \\\"those who go and don't return will have a vertical son.\\\" Such words are so resounding that you have excellent martial arts and both wisdom and courage, but you can't change your impatient temper. You didn't panic about Qin Wuyang in the hall. With your intelligence, you eliminated the wariness of the king of Qin. Although the assassination failed, your spirit and courage are admirable. You have fulfilled your mission and fulfilled your obligations. Responsibility, you did it.\\n\\n \\n\\nResponsibility, let our hearts surging!\\n\\n \\n\\nBa Jin's confession\\n\\n \\n\\nWhen walking alone in the dark, when exploring in the jagged teeth, when condemning under the uneasiness of conscience. You don't resent others, because you know who caused your fault. In the dark night, brother Bao's bow woke you up. You go back to your dream at midnight. You are so upset. Brother Bao's appearance is still so clear in your heart. You confess your mistakes because you are a responsible person. Responsibility makes you feel guilty and calls for humanity.\\n\\n \\n\\nResponsibility, let us have good thoughts.\\n\\n \\n\\nResponsibility is a kind seed, which needs us to fertilize often. Everyone has a seed of \\\"responsibility\\\". Let's nurture love and let it blossom. The seed of \\\"responsibility\\\" will be more gorgeous and brilliant!\",\"timestamp\":1639148928,\"title\":\"WU FENG\"},\"digest\":\"viEYx5GG-_CKggJRyRHyySD9TOE9Ijzqx_r0v0yjvSY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x7b31B8c09dB1D081952138479c7FF47465C476c0\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"8D8j12yLgzz2wObCaU5rzAEU3UMW4ZW7N6V8GOsxnpw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3fT2Z49IGUCVYXtG-ZsyEilgzwJLP-uhcF3akt9r5P8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ZTD20TYzgqpGfFiBbyGFNTiH7rVsU4a9ylDs-65OTpJNbrXCOzR1pcHtQhl_smcXd5orZ5afzEJDWTV5E-CZ6w\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xc67967cb69b99a327d1775fbd75ffcf21ab4717d4eb38a77464d3552a71a7f3e7080320fe374ce7d586568cd255eee933debdd9a57a34346473d151b08fcf13e1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"8D8j12yLgzz2wObCaU5rzAEU3UMW4ZW7N6V8GOsxnpw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3fT2Z49IGUCVYXtG-ZsyEilgzwJLP-uhcF3akt9r5P8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"viEYx5GG-_CKggJRyRHyySD9TOE9Ijzqx_r0v0yjvSY\"}"